<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>毕业季 on 素履独行</title><link>/tags/%E6%AF%95%E4%B8%9A%E5%AD%A3/</link><description>Recent content in 毕业季 on 素履独行</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2015 10:45:51 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="/tags/%E6%AF%95%E4%B8%9A%E5%AD%A3/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>当梦想照进现实</title><link>/posts/%E5%BD%93%E6%A2%A6%E6%83%B3%E7%85%A7%E8%BF%9B%E7%8E%B0%E5%AE%9E/</link><pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2015 10:45:51 +0000</pubDate><guid>/posts/%E5%BD%93%E6%A2%A6%E6%83%B3%E7%85%A7%E8%BF%9B%E7%8E%B0%E5%AE%9E/</guid><description>&lt;p>回到学校将近一周了，工作依然没有着落。每天穿梭在校园里，看着身边熙熙攘攘的人群来来往往，面对着许许多多陌生的面孔，看着太阳每天的起起落落，听着校园广播吟唱那些恍若隔世的时光。我深切地感受到作为一名即将毕业的大四学生，此时此刻站在这里是多么的多余。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>